entries.femaleVariant: Hello, we haven't met. I'm Elizabeth.
My husband and I, we need a somewhat delicate matter... handled. We think you could help.
This is Ward. Who'm I talkin' to?
Name's V. Lookin' into the death of one Lucius Rhyne.
Wonder why… You're not a cop.
So, about Rhyne – got a pretty good idea what happened.
Great. Come by, please. It's a sensitive matter, I'd rather discuss it face to face.
Why call me of all people?
Why call me of all people? Any particular reason?
Can't commit just now. Busy like I've never been. It'd be unwise.
V. I'm glad you called back.
Yep. Let's meet.
Your husband – who is he?
What's this about?
Nope. Got no time now, too busy.
What's so delicate about the matter?
Mind my askin' who your husband is? Actually... who're you?
Sure. Let's do that.
I'd rather not discuss details over the phone. Please, meet with us. We'll explain everything.
You came recommended.
I'd rather not say, not over the phone. Is there any way we could meet, discuss some details?
As I said, it's a rather delicate matter.
I'd rather discuss that in person, if you don't mind.
Can we meet?
I'll send you the address. See you.
I see... Well, I shouldn't discount the urgency, but I guess we could wait a couple more days. We'd really rather work with you.
Try to squeeze us in and give me a call.
I really hoped you'd see the sense of it. I assume you're ready now to meet, talk about the job?
We'll be waiting.
Workin' for the Peralezes.
Conductin' a private investigation.
I know you tried to warn the mayor.
Jefferson and Elizabeth Peralez hired me to do it.
I'm conductin' a private investigation into this... matter.
entries.maleVariant: I'm conducting a private investigation into this... matter.

entries.femaleVariant: Listen, I know you tried to warn Rhyne about the cyberpsycho.
All right. I'm headed to Chubby Buffalo's.
Be there stat.
Presumptive mayor sniffing around his predecessor's untimely death? Interesting.
Done some digging, got more intel. Also interesting.
What else do you know?
That you'd best meet with me.
entries.maleVariant: Eh, that you'd best meet with me.

entries.femaleVariant: Good luck with that. And do me a favor – lose this number. I like PIs about as much as I like the scop at Caliente.
I'm no PI.
Cops and PIs work together all the time.
I'm no private eye.
Thought private-Is worked with cops all the time. And vice versa.
So what are you?
Well, they do, all the time. In New Hollywood.
So, since you're not a dick – who are you?
Meet me. You'll find out.
Yeah, who by?
